Deputy General Manager Job in Dubai
Posted: Yesterday
CAREER OPPORTUNITY WITH SNTTA EMIR TOURS - DEPUTY GENERAL MANAGER - SNTTA Emir Tours is one of the leading Destination Management Companies in the UAE. It is a member of the UAE-based Liberty Investment Company (Liberty Group). To spearhead our expansion, we seek to immediately fill the above position. Profile: - The ideal candidate will have a Masters Degree from a recognized university and be a highly motivated leader with extraordinary planning and negotiation skills to develop business in the regional and European markets. Responsibilities: To support the General Manager by overseeing inbound tourism operations, creating and introducing new tour packages, developing strategies for Tour Consultants to increase sales and achieve targets. He will also be responsible for budgeting, implementation and contracting with overseas agents, wholesalers and developing online booking systems. We are looking for a thorough professional with minimum 10 years experience in the leisure industry. He should be able to demonstrate a proven track record of driving business growth and building strong customer relationships. He should also be skilled in the use of IT systems. Fluency in English is essential and knowledge of one or more European languages will be an added advantage. The position, which is based in Dubai, reports to the General Manager and will require international travel on a regular basis. Interested candidates who fit the profile may kindly email their CV with a recent photograph to: -
- SNTTA - Emir Tours
